2.13.21  4:54 pm   Is there a hidden message with your first YouTube vid. Die

     yes, the hidden message in that song is, if you are feeling too overwhelmed with the songwriting process, try writing the absolute shortest song you can. try to write something 1 second long. And, for the video, the message there is, if you are feeling overwhelmed with the video making process, try starting with the shortest song you have

     and your last before here comes the sun. Everyone?

     the one before "here comes the sun" was called "might quit", although admittedly it probably should have been called "it's the first day of school". the meaning behind that one, if i could tie it into the other one, is that i seem to have finally got the hang of making songs/videos that are a more reasonable length. although i still wish i could do it much faster, so that way i would be able to make many more of them

     (this is from a YouTuber that commented this)

If it's a guitar, try pressing the D, G, and B strings all on the second fret at the same time. then try the same thing but switch the B string to 3rd fret B string and keep the others the same
